[
  {
    "content_id": 671178,
    "reference_id": 14367,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:1–2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001001-53001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅遵循了古代書信寫作的傳統，但他沒使用常用的問候語（希臘文chairein），而是祝福他們有恩惠（希臘文charis）和平安。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:1",
          "end_ref": "53001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671183,
    "reference_id": 14372,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>神——我們的父與主耶穌基督</span>作為恩惠和平安的來源，是同等的。帖撒羅尼迦信徒的盼望與神的恩惠緊密相連（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16\">2:16</a>），即使在迫害中他們也能經歷神所賜的平安（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:16\">3:16</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:2",
          "end_ref": "53001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671185,
    "reference_id": 14374,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>親愛的弟兄姊妹們（譯註：和合本譯為「<span>弟兄們</span>」）：希臘文adelphoi是指同一家族中的成員，這詞涵蓋了男性和女性。</p></li><li><p>感謝神：保羅在書信開頭為帖撒羅尼迦信徒的信心、愛和「忍耐」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">1:4）</a>感恩。<span>儘管經歷逼迫</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:5\">帖後1:5</a>），這些基本的基督徒美德（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:13\">林前13:13</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:4-Col1:5\">西1:4–5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:21-Heb10:24\">來10:21–24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1-1Pet2:22\">彼前2:1–22</a>）仍在教會中日漸成熟。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:3",
          "end_ref": "53001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671184,
    "reference_id": 14373,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:3–10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001003-53001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在為帖撒羅尼迦教會感謝神之後（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3-2Thess1:4\">1:3–4</a>），保羅提到迫害（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">1:4</a>），自他的第一封信以來這些迫害已經加劇（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">帖前1:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">2:14</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:3-1Thess3:4\">3:3–4</a>）。神將減輕他們的痛苦（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:5-2Thess1:10\">帖後1:5–10</a>）並審判逼迫他們的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:3",
          "end_ref": "53001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671186,
    "reference_id": 14375,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅為帖撒羅尼迦信徒的忍耐和信心向別的教會誇口，這會激勵教會在面對巨大的敵意時堅忍和持守忠心（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">帖前2:14</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:3-1Thess3:4\">3:3–4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:4",
          "end_ref": "53001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671187,
    "reference_id": 14376,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>蒙神呼召進入祂國度的人將因此受苦（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">徒14:22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">帖前2:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:5",
          "end_ref": "53001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671188,
    "reference_id": 14377,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>安息（譯註：和合本譯為「平安」）：從苦難中得釋放。</p></li><li><p>在別處，保羅談到基督的「降臨」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1\">2:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19\">帖前2:19</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">3:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:15\">4:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">5:23）</a>；在這裡，他稱這是主耶穌的「顯現」或「顯露」，是現今無法用肉眼看見的（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7-1Pet1:8\">彼前1:7–8</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">4:13）</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:7",
          "end_ref": "53001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671189,
    "reference_id": 14378,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>他們會因拒絕關於基督的信息而受刑罰（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8\">1:8）</a>。</p></li><li><p><span>永遠的沉淪</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">帖前5:3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">提前6:9</a>）是無法改變的。</p></li><li><p><span>離開主的面</span>指即將到來的審判之來源（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:10\">賽2:10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19\">19</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">21）</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:9",
          "end_ref": "53001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671179,
    "reference_id": 14368,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>那日子：主的日子（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:2\">2:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:2-1Thess5:4\">帖前5:2–4</a>；見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203237\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesThemes\">主的日子</span>」主題註釋）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:10",
          "end_ref": "53001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 203237,
          "content_id": 700300,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesThemes",
          "label": "耶和華的日子",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671181,
    "reference_id": 14370,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><span>看你們配得過所蒙的召</span>：保羅之前就提醒過帖撒羅尼迦信徒，神呼召他們要以「神看為配得」的方式行事為人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">帖前2:12</a>；另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">弗4:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">腓1:27</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">西1:10</a>）。</p></li><li><p>保羅祈求神賜予帖撒羅尼迦基督徒能力，以討神喜悅的方式行事為人。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:11",
          "end_ref": "53001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671180,
    "reference_id": 14369,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:11–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001011-53001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅向帖撒羅尼迦信徒保證神所應許的公義，無論是對他們還是對迫害他們的人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:5-2Thess1:10\">1:5–10</a>）。<span>因為將來的得救意味著要履行當下的責任</span>，所以保羅禱告他們在基督再來時被視為是配得的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:11",
          "end_ref": "53001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671182,
    "reference_id": 14371,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然我們主耶穌的名被帖撒羅尼迦的迫害者棄絕（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8\">1:8</a>），但耶穌最終將因信徒的生命得榮耀。此外，他們也將與祂一同得榮耀（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:14\">2:14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">帖前2:12</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:18\">羅8:17–18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">西3:4</a>）。參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:5\">以賽亞書六十六章5節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:12",
          "end_ref": "53001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671197,
    "reference_id": 14386,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>我們主耶穌基督降臨時</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7-2Thess1:10\">1:7–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19\">帖前2:19</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">3:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:15-1Thess5:2\">4:15–5:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">5:23</a>），祂所有的子民都將聚集在一起來迎接祂。這將發生在教會復活和被提之時（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:18\">帖前4:13–18）</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:1",
          "end_ref": "53002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671190,
    "reference_id": 14379,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:1–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002001-53002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>關於主的日子的錯誤教導擾亂了帖撒羅尼迦教會（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1-2Thess2:2\">2:1–2</a>）。保羅提醒他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:5\">2:5</a>），在那日子之前會有兩件事發生：一次大的離道反教的事和<span>大罪人顯露出來</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:12\">2:3–12</a>）。基督再來時將毀滅這人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2:3</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">8</a>），而那些受騙的人也將被定罪（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9-2Thess2:12\">2:9–12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:1",
          "end_ref": "53002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671198,
    "reference_id": 14387,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>帖撒羅尼迦的基督徒曾問過保羅主的日子何時會來（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:1-1Thess5:11\">帖前5:1–11</a>）。但有一個錯誤的教導說這日子已經來了（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:18\">提後2:18</a>），這使他們的信心動搖並感到恐懼。</p></li><li><p><span>有靈、有言語、有……書信</span>：這教導的來源可能是一個虛假的預言（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:2\">約一4:1–2</a>）、一篇錯誤的講道或一封誤認為來自保羅的書信。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:2",
          "end_ref": "53002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671199,
    "reference_id": 14388,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在主的日子之前會有兩件事發生（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:2\">2:2</a>）。</p><ul><li><p>猶太教和基督教神學都預言在末日之前會有一場大<span>離道反教的事</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:11-Matt24:14\">太24:11–14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">提前4:1</a>）。</p></li><li><p>無法無天的人（譯註：和合本譯為「<span>大罪人</span>」）是不守法或反對律法的；他的特徵就是犯罪。</p></li><li><p>帶來毀滅的人（或<em>注定毀滅的人</em>；譯註：和合本譯為「沉淪之子」）：這裡的重點在於那罪人自身的毀滅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">帖後2:8</a>），而不是他所帶來的毀滅。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:3",
          "end_ref": "53002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671200,
    "reference_id": 14389,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><span>高擡自己</span>：和其它羅馬城市一樣，帖撒羅尼迦建造了供奉君王的廟宇。這種崇拜是此處所描述的崇拜的原型。</p></li><li><p><span>甚至坐在神的殿裏</span>：<span>安提阿古·伊皮法尼</span>（<span>Antiochus Epiphanes</span>）在公元前167年褻瀆了耶路撒冷聖殿（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:27\">但9:27</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:31\">11:31</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:11\">12:11</a>）這可能預表了此預言中的事件（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:15\">太24:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:14\">可13:14</a>）。或者，這可能是指在公元40年被稱為「顯現的新神」的皇帝卡理古拉（Caligula）試圖在聖殿中設立自己的像。另一個可能是，這裡所說的<em>殿</em>可能是為不法之人建造的帝國神廟（<em>神的</em>也可理解為<em>諸神的</em>），而不一定是重建於耶路撒冷的聖殿。</p></li><li><p><span>自稱是神</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:2-Ezek28:10\">結28:2–10</a>）：在公元第一世紀時，將神聖的頭銜賦予君王是很常見的。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:4",
          "end_ref": "53002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671201,
    "reference_id": 14390,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>那攔阻他的是甚麼</span>：對於這一點有各種不同的解釋，有人認為這是指神、聖靈、教會、福音、保羅、皇帝、羅馬帝國或政府。另一種解釋認為，這個用語可能是指在不法的人之前出現的某事物或某人，是當時活躍的不法之人的代理者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:7-2Thess2:8\">2:7–8</a>）；在希臘文學中，這個表達方式可用來描述被邪靈附身。<span>當時機成熟時，這個人物會為那不法之人鋪路</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2:3</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">8</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:6",
          "end_ref": "53002006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671202,
    "reference_id": 14391,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><span>那不法之人的力量</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:6\">2:3–6</a>）已經秘密地發動了，這就像在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18\">約翰一書二章18節</a>中那敵基督的一樣。</p></li><li><p>秘密地（希臘文mustērion；譯註：和合本譯為「隱意」）：這是神秘宗教儀式中<span>常用來描述儀式的詞語</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:6\">帖後2:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>發動：這表示了超自然的干預，無論是來自神的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">帖前2:13</a>）還是像此處一樣是來自惡者的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">帖後2:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">弗2:2</a>）。</p></li><li><p><span>有一個攔阻的可能是指反對那不法之人的某個人；也可能是指一位被附身者；或者是指那位附身者——撒但</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">帖後2:9</a>；見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"14390\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">2:6研讀註釋</span>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:7",
          "end_ref": "53002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 14390,
          "content_id": 671201,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:6",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671203,
    "reference_id": 14392,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅宣告了<span>不法的人終將</span>毀滅（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2:3</a>）。雖然這個人自稱為神，<span>高抬自己超過一切受人敬拜的</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:4\">2:4</a>），並從撒但那裡獲得了能力（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">2:9</a>），但主耶穌將會猛烈而徹底地摧毀他（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:4\">賽11:4</a>）。</p></li><li><p>榮光：這是指基督的顯現（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:14\">提前6:14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">提後1:10</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1\">4:1</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13\">多2:13</a>），是另一種描述基督再來（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1\">帖後2:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19\">帖前2:19</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">3:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:15\">4:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">5:23</a>）或顯現（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7\">帖後1:7</a>）的方式。在古代文學中，<em>顯現</em>是指神祇顯靈或展現神聖力量來激發人的崇拜。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:8",
          "end_ref": "53002008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671204,
    "reference_id": 14393,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>就像基督將以君王的神聖大能顯現一樣（his parousia；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1\">2:1</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19\">帖前2:19</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">3:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:15\">4:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">5:23</a>），這個人物也同樣會以君王般的姿態來臨（parousia）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:9",
          "end_ref": "53002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671191,
    "reference_id": 14380,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>如同在其它經文中所讀到的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:12\">出9:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:22\">代下18:22</a>），<span>神有時會任憑人被他們所渴望、用來取代真理的罪或迷惑的權勢所掌控</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">羅1:24</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:26\">26</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28\">28</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:8\">11:8</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:11",
          "end_ref": "53002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671192,
    "reference_id": 14381,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他們將被定罪（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:6-2Thess1:9\">1:6–9</a>），因為他們不信真理（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:10\">2:10</a>），反而相信那不法之人的謊言（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9-2Thess2:10\">2:9–10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:12",
          "end_ref": "53002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:12"
        }
      ],
