    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671193,
    "reference_id": 14382,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>祂呼召你們進入救恩（譯註：和合本譯為「<span>召你們到這地步</span>」）：神透過福音的傳講呼召祂的選民歸向自己（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11\">1:11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">帖前2:12</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7\">4:7</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:24\">5:24</a>）。</p></li><li><p>因信仰而受苦的人最終將同享我們主耶穌基督的榮光（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">羅5:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:18\">8:17–18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">西1:27</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">帖前2:12</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:14",
          "end_ref": "53002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671194,
    "reference_id": 14383,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>自從帖撒羅尼迦教會設立以來，保羅一直在關心他們的信心是否堅定（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:2\">帖前3:2</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:5\">5</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:8\">8</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1-1Thess4:2\">4:1–2</a>）以及他們是否遵行他的教導（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6\">帖後3:6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:2\">林前11:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3\">15:3</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">猶1:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:15",
          "end_ref": "53002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671195,
    "reference_id": 14384,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>永遠的安慰並……盼望</span>超越了死亡和<span>對近期未來的不確定性</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:16",
          "end_ref": "53002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671196,
    "reference_id": 14385,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅的禱告回應了提摩太探訪教會的目的——在信仰上堅固並鼓勵帖撒羅尼迦的信徒（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:2\">帖前3:2</a>)。</p></li><li><p>安慰你們的心不僅僅意味著<em>勸慰</em>，而是在他們的恐懼和疑慮中<em>勸勉</em>或<em>鼓勵</em>他們 (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1-2Thess2:12\">帖後2:1–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:18\">帖前4:18</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:11\">5:11</a>)。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:17",
          "end_ref": "53002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671214,
    "reference_id": 14403,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>禱告：這是在祈求福音能夠盡快傳揚開來，這讓人想起<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:15\">詩篇一四七篇5節</a>。保羅用競賽來談論這個意象（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:26\">林前9:24–26</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:2\">加2:2</a>），競賽中的勝利者會得著榮耀。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:1",
          "end_ref": "53003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671205,
    "reference_id": 14394,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:1–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003001-53003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在進入書信的最後一個主題之前（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6-2Thess3:15\">3:6–15</a>），保羅請求他們為他禱告（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:1-2Thess3:2\">3:1–2</a>），並向帖撒羅尼迦信徒確保了神在患難中的保護（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3-2Thess3:5\">3:3–5</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:1",
          "end_ref": "53003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671215,
    "reference_id": 14404,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅也為了福音而受苦（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">林後6:5</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:26\">11:23–26</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">帖前2:2</a>）。他祈求得著拯救的禱告呼應了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4\">以賽亞書二十五章4節</a>的內容。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:2",
          "end_ref": "53003002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671216,
    "reference_id": 14405,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>帖撒羅尼迦信徒所遭受的苦難是那惡者（或<em>邪惡</em>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">2:9</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4-2Thess1:6\">1:4–6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">帖前1:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">2:14</a>）所造成的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:3",
          "end_ref": "53003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671217,
    "reference_id": 14406,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這個求神引導（字面意思是<em>使……正直</em>）他們的心的禱告，反映出舊約聖經中的一個表達方式（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:18\">代上29:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:19\">箴23:19</a>）。基督徒應該像神一樣去愛，並像基督那樣實踐恆久的忍耐。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:5",
          "end_ref": "53003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671219,
    "reference_id": 14408,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅的吩咐是出於主耶穌基督的權柄（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:2\">帖前4:2</a>）。</p></li><li><p>教會成員應該遠離懶惰的基督徒（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:7\">帖後3:7</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:11-2Thess3:13\">11–13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">帖前5:14</a>）。<span>遠離懶惰的人會對他們產生</span>深刻的印象（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:17\">太18:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17\">羅16:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:9-1Cor5:13\">林前5:9–13</a>），促使他們感到羞愧（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:14\">帖後3:14</a>）並悔改，但<span>並不等同於將他們逐出教會</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:15\">3:15</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:6",
          "end_ref": "53003006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671218,
    "reference_id": 14407,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:6–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003006-53003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在之前的書信中，保羅已經提到了那些拒絕工作的懶惰的教會成員的問題（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11-1Thess4:12\">帖前4:11–12</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">5:14</a>）。有些人忽視了他的信息和榜樣，因此他提供了額外的指示來應付這些成員。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:6",
          "end_ref": "53003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671220,
    "reference_id": 14409,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以身作則在古代世界中<span>被高度重視</span>。保羅自己就是親手勞作以供應自己的飲食，以成為他們的榜樣（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:8\">3:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:9\">帖前2:9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:7",
          "end_ref": "53003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671221,
    "reference_id": 14410,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>白吃人的飯</span>：雖然保羅教導基督教會的工人可以因服事而獲得報酬（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:9\">3:9</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:10\">太10:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:7-1Cor9:14\">林前9:7–14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">提前5:17–18</a>），<span>他並沒有行使那項權利</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:9\">帖前2:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6-2Thess3:10\">帖後3:6–10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:8",
          "end_ref": "53003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671222,
    "reference_id": 14411,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅遠離<span>當時那些受名聲和金錢驅使的人</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:5\">帖前2:5</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:9",
          "end_ref": "53003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671206,
    "reference_id": 14395,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>工作是謀生的正當方式</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">創3:17–19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:2\">詩128:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4\">箴10:4</a>）。保羅不讓教會承擔餵養<span>那些拒絕工作的信徒</span>的責任。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:10",
          "end_ref": "53003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671207,
    "reference_id": 14396,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅藉著主耶穌的權柄強調這勸誡的重要性（如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6\">3:6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1-1Thess4:2\">帖前4:1–2</a>）。</p></li><li><p>安定下來（譯註：和合本譯為「<span>安靜</span>」）：即過安靜的生活，而不是多管閒事（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">帖前4:11</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:12",
          "end_ref": "53003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671208,
    "reference_id": 14397,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>行善：帖撒羅尼迦人被勸勉去幫助那些真正有需要的人（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9-Gal6:10\">加6:9–10</a>），與那些懶惰和依賴他人的人形成對比（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:7-2Thess3:8\">帖後3:7–8</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:10\">10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:13",
          "end_ref": "53003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671209,
    "reference_id": 14398,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅希望那悖逆的基督徒<span>在被群體排斥後，會感到羞愧並悔改</span>（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"14408\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">3:6研讀註釋</span>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:14",
          "end_ref": "53003014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 14408,
          "content_id": 671219,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:6",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671210,
    "reference_id": 14399,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>不要以他為仇人</span>：在古代世界中，人會斷絕與敵對者的社會關係，並對他們採取懲罰的行動。保羅警告帖撒羅尼迦信徒，對不順服的基督徒的懲戒（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:14\">3:14</a>）不應變成這樣的攻擊。相反，<span>教會應當以家人身份對待他們，希望他們能改正自己的行為</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:12\">帖前5:12</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">14</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:15",
          "end_ref": "53003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671211,
    "reference_id": 14400,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這最後的禱告呼應了耶穌在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">約翰福音十四章27節</a>中的祝福（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:26\">民6:26</a>），<span>這與這些信徒在帖撒羅尼迦所面對的情況形成對比</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4-2Thess1:10\">帖後1:4–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">帖前2:14</a>）。保羅始終明白主耶穌與祂的百姓同在（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:33\">羅15:33</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">腓4:9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:16",
          "end_ref": "53003016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671212,
    "reference_id": 14401,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>一位代筆者為保羅執筆寫了這封信（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:22\">羅16:22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">彼前5:12</a>）。現在保羅親自執筆加上了最後的問候（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:21\">林前16:21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:11\">加6:11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:18\">西4:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:19\">門1:19</a>）。因為他懷疑有一封並不出自他手的書信以他的名義流傳（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:2\">帖後2:2</a>），<span>他強調這個驗證方式，是為了證明這封信確實是出自他本人。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:17",
          "end_ref": "53003017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671213,
    "reference_id": 14402,
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦後書 3:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "53003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>古代書信常以對健康或富足的祝福作為結尾，但保羅的祝福更加宏大：他呼求主耶穌基督賜恩給收信人（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:28\">帖前5:28</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "53003018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:18",
          "end_ref": "53003018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TH 3:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
]